data.text: @damiandugdale Hi, In usual cases the handling time is up to 8 weeks and our customer care department will contact you when they have handled you case. I would recommend that you make an edit to your tweet and delete the personal information. Kind regards, Anne

@danmichalczyk Hi again, You can not book regular Business class for points with a Fly Premium Voucher. You can only book bonus trips (the ones with a gold circle above) with your Fly Premium Voucher. Kind regards, Anne

@Yalemisew Hi, I'm sorry you didn't receive your bags. You must report missing bags here https://t.co/ojhL9dIf2x if you haven't done this at the airport already. You can track your bags here https://t.co/2zwsPbhQFU or contact baggage service here https://t.co/We1FdD7ZiM 
Kind regards, Anne

@danmichalczyk Hi, You will see your Fly Premium Voucher as an option in the booking flow, so you must click on the voucher for it to be activated. It wont be automatically applied. 
Kind regards, Anne

@Christi17088775 Hi, If you have received a case ID, your case is registered in our system. We have deployed all the resources we can to speed up the process and deal with all cases in turn. If anything further needs to be completed, we will contact you. Kind regards, Anne
